Subject: Re: [T2] New 71, coupla issues

Review the distributor and carb articles in the
type2.com library.  One discusses all that you need to
check before assuming that your distributor needs to
be replaced, but the same holds true for the carb. 
Ie, cracked manifold boots or other sources of vac
leak must be checked.

